# Mobile Testing Test Cases

## Scope
Ensures web/app works smoothly on mobile devices.

---

## TC_MOB_001 – Responsive Layout
Expected: No UI breaks, layout adjusts correctly.

## TC_MOB_002 – Touch Interaction
Expected: Buttons are clickable, gestures work smoothly.

## TC_MOB_003 – Slow Network Handling
Expected: Clear loading indicators, no app crash.

## TC_MOB_004 – Orientation Change
Expected: Data not lost when rotating device.

## TC_MOB_005 – Performance
Expected: Smooth scrolling, no lag or freeze.
